<br>
Engage -&gt; Right position: Jaelen's Katana + Shield<br>
Right position -&gt; Fatass dead: Bloodfrenzy + Blade of Carnage<br>
Fatass dead -&gt; Blob dead: Bloodfrenzy + Shield (no aggro hitches either)<br>
<br>
